parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the parking brake can cause the vehicle to roll or move unexpectedly, even when the parking brake is engaged, which can lead to accidents or injuries.
symptoms: The vehicle rolls or moves when the parking brake is engaged
the vehicle will not shift into gear
the parking brake does not hold as well as it should.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the spare tire carrier hoist can cause the spare tire to drop down, potentially causing damage to the vehicle's underside, and creating a road hazard, which can lead to accidents or injuries.
symptoms: The spare tire drops down below the chassis
the spare tire carrier hoist becomes loose
the spare tire is not properly secured.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Tag Axle to Frame Fastener Failure
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the bolt and self-locking nut assembly holding the tag axle to the frame can cause the tag axle to become loose, potentially leading to loss of control, accidents, or injuries.
symptoms: The bolt and self-locking nut assembly becomes loose
unusual noises or vibrations from the rear of the vehicle.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the automatic parking brake system can cause the vehicle to roll unexpectedly, potentially leading to accidents, injuries, or fatalities, especially if the vehicle rolls into traffic.
symptoms: The vehicle rolls unexpectedly while in auto park
the auto brake light comes on
the auto brake fails to engage
the vehicle moves without driver input.
